WEBVTT

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.000
Liu... Liu... Liu...

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:18.400
He's dead!

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.280
Master Liu!

00:02:33.439 --> 00:02:34.439
Everyone, step back a bit.

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:35.120
Step back.

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:36.719
Let my good apprentice...

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.319
examine the corpse properly.

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:47.639
Well?

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.520
Master Liu was stabbed multiple times.

00:02:50.199 --> 00:02:52.199
The weapon appears to be a dagger...

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:53.360
about one foot eight long.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.360
The head was severed after death.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:57.960
There isn't much bleeding at the cut.

00:02:58.719 --> 00:02:59.319
And the time of death?

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:00.840
Approximately two hours ago.

00:03:01.719 --> 00:03:02.560
Around 9 p.m.

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:12.560
At around 9 p.m...

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:14.120
Didn't we just part ways then?

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:18.960
We were chatting with Divine Doctor Du and his apprentice.

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:20.479
That's right.

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:24.039
Besides Master Liu...

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:26.039
these three ladies were the only ones absent, right?

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:28.599
After leaving the main hall,

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:31.280
I was in the backyard with my father the whole time.

00:03:31.639 --> 00:03:32.560
You were in the backyard?

00:03:33.199 --> 00:03:33.919
Are there witnesses?

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:37.080
Mr. Zhang saw me.

00:03:38.759 --> 00:03:39.639
Yes, yes.

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:43.000
And this one...

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:45.599
Ah Kun.

00:03:46.439 --> 00:03:48.159
Known in the Jianghu as Master Kun.

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:49.680
Master Kun.

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:52.159
May I be so bold as to ask,

00:03:52.719 --> 00:03:53.759
who are you exactly?

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:55.000
To be suspecting us here?

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:59.159
Aren't you and your master suspects yourselves?

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:00.280
Yeah!

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:01.520
Who do you think you are?

00:04:01.719 --> 00:04:02.960
Asking all these questions.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:06.479
I think you master and apprentice are the most suspicious.

00:04:10.879 --> 00:04:11.879
I fall ill at nightfall.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:12.840
Everyone knows that.

00:04:14.199 --> 00:04:15.360
So I had my apprentice...

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.879
lock me in the woodshed.

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:18.560
That rules me out.

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:22.439
Can one just rule oneself out?

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:24.319
I can testify.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:25.839
At that time,

00:04:26.279 --> 00:04:27.920
I delivered dinner to Divine Doctor Du.

00:04:28.399 --> 00:04:29.519
He indeed could not leave.

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.279
And what about you, Master Kun?

00:04:34.439 --> 00:04:35.600
The two of us were together.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:42.360
The Flirt.

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:43.560
What about it?

00:04:44.319 --> 00:04:45.079
Is that a problem?

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:49.399
Are there any other witnesses?

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:51.639
We were together.

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:55.680
Why would we need anyone else?

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:58.600
Ridiculous.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:04:59.759
Truly ridiculous.

00:05:00.439 --> 00:05:01.279
What secret code?

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:02.720
I'm done solving it.

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:04.680
I don't want to die here.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:05.639
I'm leaving.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:07.240
There is miasma in the dense forest.

00:05:07.519 --> 00:05:09.199
It won't be too late to leave at dawn tomorrow.

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:10.519
Brother Zhang Shan.

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:11.759
Don't rush to your death.

00:05:12.519 --> 00:05:14.040
Miss Xiao Bai, do you have a Poison-Warding Pill?

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:15.519
I have one here.

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:20.480
Apprentice, stop him!

00:05:22.399 --> 00:05:23.079
Go!

00:05:26.959 --> 00:05:28.480
Don't try any tricks with me.

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:32.959
Young Master.

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.360
Master Liu's room is a critical crime scene.

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:37.040
Please be sure to have it guarded well.

00:05:37.319 --> 00:05:38.199
Rest assured, Divine Doctor Du.

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:51.120
Hero Zhang.

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:03.839
You...

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:43.439
Not good

00:06:43.920 --> 00:06:45.160
This mist causes hallucinations

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:47.279
Must stay awake

00:06:53.480 --> 00:06:54.000
Disciple, this...

00:06:56.319 --> 00:06:57.279
What's the situation?

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:58.160
What is going on?

00:06:58.959 --> 00:07:00.160
Why did you come back alone?

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.600
Hero Zhang was hit by the poison miasma

00:07:03.519 --> 00:07:04.319
He committed suicide

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.519
What's wrong with him?

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:08.279
Quickly, make him drink this

00:07:08.439 --> 00:07:09.319
He's been poisoned by the miasma

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:12.800
Quickly, help him back to his room to rest

00:07:18.839 --> 00:07:21.959
We should have dragged him back for interrogation

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:24.199
Could Zhang Shan have committed suicide out of fear of punishment?

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:25.879
Why is this miasma so potent?

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:29.519
Wumei Valley was originally just a dense forest

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.439
Later, to protect the manor...

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:32.600
...from being coveted by outsiders...

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:35.040
...the Master raised many poisonous creatures in the forest

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:36.839
They grew wildly in the forest

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:38.279
That is how the miasma came to be

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:39.399
Anyone who is poisoned...

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:41.120
...will go mad at best...

00:07:41.439 --> 00:07:42.480
...or die instantly at worst

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:44.519
The poison gas is heaviest at night

00:07:44.879 --> 00:07:47.040
Even the Poison-Warding Pill cannot guarantee safety

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.040
We took the pills when we arrived yesterday

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.439
Then why did we still get poisoned?

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.399
The pills the manor distributes to guests...

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:54.800
...are only effective for two hours

00:07:55.399 --> 00:07:56.800
Just enough for you to cross the dense forest...

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:57.920
...and reach the manor

00:07:58.759 --> 00:08:00.000
Then why does the forest's miasma...

00:08:00.279 --> 00:08:01.120
...not enter the manor?

00:08:01.439 --> 00:08:03.519
The plants in the manor can resist the poison miasma

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:06.720
The timber used for buildings was also repeatedly soaked in medicinal juices

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:08.439
As long as you don't leave the manor...

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:09.959
...you will be safe

00:08:10.879 --> 00:08:11.720
I see

00:08:11.839 --> 00:08:12.720
I see

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:16.160
As for Zhang Shan's body...

00:08:16.399 --> 00:08:18.399
...I must ask the Young Master to send someone to retrieve it tomorrow

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.920
I'll send someone as soon as it's light

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.079
This matter is not simple

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:23.800
I think everyone should rest first

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:24.839
That sounds good

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:26.240
Farewell

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:26.959
Farewell

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:28.160
Let's go, let's go

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:28.879
Hurry, hurry

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:36.679
Lord Hua, you're awake

00:08:45.799 --> 00:08:46.279
Here

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:47.679
Drink the medicine while it's hot

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.639
What kind of medicine would you give me?

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.600
Gut-rotting poison, one sip kills

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:54.799
More toxic than the miasma

00:08:57.279 --> 00:08:58.360
Go get me a piece of paper

00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:05.399
Here

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:16.639
Lord Hua

00:09:17.679 --> 00:09:20.000
You're sending a message to Dali Temple, aren't you?

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:22.279
Fine

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:23.639
I won't look

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:25.200
I won't look

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:42.039
Miss Xiao Bai

00:09:43.279 --> 00:09:44.120
Watching the moon?

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:45.039
Concubine Si

00:09:46.679 --> 00:09:47.919
I'm not that delicate

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:48.759
No need to stand on ceremony

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:50.000
Concubine Si

00:09:50.440 --> 00:09:51.679
Why are you still awake so late?

00:09:52.039 --> 00:09:54.000
I've been having nightmares lately

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.120
I can't sleep well

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:57.480
And this Sedative is too bitter

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:59.279
So I went to the kitchen...

00:09:59.879 --> 00:10:01.600
...and made a bowl of red date and longan soup

00:10:02.039 --> 00:10:03.159
To eat mixed with the Sedative

00:10:04.039 --> 00:10:04.600
It's not bitter

00:10:07.559 --> 00:10:08.279
Concubine Si

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:10.639
Today...

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:12.600
...someone...

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.399
...said I look like a good friend of his

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:18.720
People who talk like that...

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:21.759
...are mostly philanderers

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.879
I've seen plenty of men

00:10:25.320 --> 00:10:27.039
These tricks to deceive young girls...

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:28.120
...are not to be trusted

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:34.200
I think he...

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:36.559
...probably isn't

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:43.519
Lord Hua

00:10:44.759 --> 00:10:45.360
Master Kun

00:10:46.279 --> 00:10:46.879
How about...

00:10:47.679 --> 00:10:48.559
...you scoot over a bit?

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.639
I'll get on the bed, let's squeeze together

00:10:53.799 --> 00:10:55.480
I helped cure your poison and treat your wounds, after all

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:56.919
Is this how you repay me?

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.440
Then go back to the woodshed

00:10:59.279 --> 00:11:00.240
There's plenty of space there

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:01.679
No need

00:11:40.559 --> 00:11:41.000
My Lord

00:11:43.799 --> 00:11:44.200
My Lord

00:11:44.759 --> 00:11:45.519
A letter from Master Kun.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.159
With such a good show,

00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:56.000
Lord Nine Thousand Years would surely be interested.

00:11:56.799 --> 00:11:58.240
Send it to the Crown Prince immediately.

00:11:58.480 --> 00:11:58.879
Yes, sir.

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:07.720
Everyone,

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.240
it rained last night,

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:10.399
so it is stuffy indoors.

00:12:10.759 --> 00:12:11.879
It is fresher out in the courtyard,

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:14.039
so I took the liberty

00:12:14.279 --> 00:12:15.720
of moving breakfast here.

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:17.840
Thank you, Young Master.

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:18.840
Please, have a seat.

00:12:18.919 --> 00:12:19.360
Sit down.

00:12:28.519 --> 00:12:29.840
You all had a fright last night.

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:31.080
I apologize for the poor hospitality.

00:12:31.159 --> 00:12:31.960
I am truly sorry.

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:34.360
After breakfast,

00:12:34.600 --> 00:12:36.159
I will distribute the Poison-Warding Pills.

00:12:36.679 --> 00:12:38.480
You can leave around 9 a.m.

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:41.600
As for the murders in the manor,

00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:43.639
what does the Young Master plan to do?

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:45.200
Report to the authorities, naturally.

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:48.039
I shouldn't trouble Divine Doctor Du and his disciple.

00:12:50.320 --> 00:12:52.120
You really have no manners.

00:12:52.679 --> 00:12:54.240
You should serve tea to your master first.

00:13:01.159 --> 00:13:01.679
Master,

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:04.200
please have some tea.

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:04.840
I'll do it myself.

00:13:06.159 --> 00:13:07.320
Watch what you're doing!

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:08.759
I'm sorry.

00:13:30.759 --> 00:13:31.240
Thank you.

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:34.399
Young Master,

00:13:34.799 --> 00:13:37.080
has Hero Zhang's body been found?

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:38.559
The head is missing.

00:13:43.399 --> 00:13:45.240
Didn't you say the miasma is thick at night,

00:13:46.039 --> 00:13:46.919
keeping birds and beasts away?

00:13:47.799 --> 00:13:48.639
Where is his body?

00:13:49.320 --> 00:13:50.840
Could you take me to see it?

00:13:54.360 --> 00:13:55.200
What is that smell?

00:13:56.519 --> 00:13:57.600
It smells like medicinal herbs.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:58.679
Oh no!

00:13:59.200 --> 00:13:59.879
Myriad Treasures Pavilion!

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:04.879
You're not eating?

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:36.639
So many treasures, all burned.

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:46.120
What a pity.

00:14:46.919 --> 00:14:47.519
Indeed.

00:14:48.440 --> 00:14:49.000
Flint.

00:14:52.399 --> 00:14:52.840
The roof.

00:14:53.759 --> 00:14:54.639
Someone removed the tiles.

00:14:56.519 --> 00:14:58.600
It seems someone placed flint on this chest,

00:14:59.279 --> 00:15:00.080
removed the tiles,

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:01.960
and waited for the sunlight to shine in.

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:04.519
The flint ignited and burned this chest.

00:15:10.799 --> 00:15:11.600
This chest...

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:13.559
did it contain something valuable?

00:15:13.919 --> 00:15:14.840
Stored in here

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:16.480
were the things needed to cross the forest

00:15:16.639 --> 00:15:18.000
and resist the toxic miasma...

00:15:18.519 --> 00:15:19.159
the Poison-Warding Pills.

00:15:19.639 --> 00:15:20.279
What?

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:22.080
That means

00:15:22.759 --> 00:15:24.000
none of us can leave now.

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:25.919
How could this happen?

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:26.960
Who did this?

00:15:28.679 --> 00:15:29.559
They must have done it on purpose.

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.720
It seems someone deliberately

00:15:32.759 --> 00:15:33.879
wants to trap us here.

00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:36.600
Three murders in one night.

00:15:38.480 --> 00:15:40.279
The victims were all posed like dancers.

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:41.600
And the Poison-Warding Pills

00:15:41.879 --> 00:15:44.200
were destroyed right before distribution.

00:15:44.799 --> 00:15:46.080
It seems it's not for money,

00:15:46.919 --> 00:15:47.919
but to take lives.

00:15:52.559 --> 00:15:53.279
Guess...

00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:55.080
who will be

00:15:56.720 --> 00:15:57.600
next?